General.Name: Golden House
General.Description: Golden House Ltd engages in the management and operation of sheltered housing centers for the elderly population in Israel. It operates The Golden Age House TA, that contains 300 housing units, as well as public areas, a lobby, a club, library, cinema hall, computer room, synagogue, classrooms, lecture rooms, gym, and green garden terrace. The company also offers nursing care services. In addition, it is involved in the renting of commercial buildings. The company was incorporated in 1982 and is based in Tel Aviv-Yafo, Israel.
